com.vangav.backend.push_notifications.android

Class AndroidNotification

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vangav.backend.push_notifications.android.AndroidNotification
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class AndroidNotification
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    AndroidNotification class represents an Android Push Notification to be sent to Android devices through Google Cloud Messaging servers Serializable to be embedded into a JSON object and dispatched to a worker instance if needed Built on top of Google's gcm library --> https://github.com/google/gcm/tree/master/client-libraries/java/ rest-client/src/com/google/android/gcm/server
    See Also:
